title: Telephone Worker Interview
Application Type: I applied through college or university. I interviewed at Contact Community Services (East Syracuse, NY) in Sept 2017
Interview Descriptions: You interview with the program director and both of the supervisors for two of the primary hotline contracts. They sit roundtable style and all interview you. It was not overwhelming. It did not feel like I was being grilled. They were warm and personable.
Interview Questions: What would you say are your strengths?
